{"id": "1249669340551315457", "channel_id": "1249669340551315457", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "此篇為超維24幻夢深潛向的全面解析滿分攻略，有任何疑問或要我補充的請留言告訴我。\n\n本來是要出旺達24攻略的，因此去打了幾天的癲五，打一打發現有時候拔掉旺達會更好用，所以本篇來介紹兩種超維24的陣容。\n\n\n(更新了一下排版和字體大小，放在留言，連結如下)\nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1249669340551315457/1250049358532186112\n\n\n求點薯條🍟 \n\n\nUID:100352106\n\n2024.6.10. mob", "timestamp": "2024-06-10T10:19:48.521000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-11T13:08:51.766000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😡", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 21}, {"emoji": "finger", "emoji_id": "1234798285466632212", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1249669340551315457", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "我於癲狂之中盛放，在靜默無聲裡消逝，我是孤獨的總合——24(超維24攻略)", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179755759763526"]}
{"id": "1249719729665605643", "channel_id": "1249719729665605643", "type": 0, "author_id": "1073914607741177866", "author_name": "scholar_2", "author_bot": false, "content": "這次不是死抗戰神了，死抗次數都很正常😈 \n\n1-4：雙爆+100%。非常適合單刀，沒什麽好説的，希洛莉莉秒了，一人一刀35000帶走。\n常規小圖，1點1商；\n\n2-4：道中之神造物。可以和上一期一樣用希洛莉莉也可以用水母戈利亞抗到7回合秒了（死抗抓的三選一是什麽對於爆發很關鍵。\n常規小圖，1點1商+1隨機覺醒事件；\n\n3-4：精通狂氣造物，血肉親爹。24血厚，建議使用成長輸出或者毒隊，筆者使用尤烏特攻，問題不是很大，單段用屏障、死抗、救救我吃掉就行，多段拿盾吃。\n常規中圖，2點2商，需要規劃路線否則會被症狀封路；\n\n4-4：造物混沌隊或者鑰令增幅大的陣容都不錯，提供很多費用。海德拉主要特點是五次大招給你一次高額四連擊，二階段有召喚物和自身會上很多debuff和封印，不建議使用需要頻繁釋放大招的隊伍，應對建議是兩種，一是二階段在她封印出手前（普通四連擊會帶一個封印）就秒殺，二是生存能力很强抗過去再反殺（比如旺達降攻、戈利亞吸力量等）當然也可以帶艾爾瓦反制。\n非常規中圖，2點1商，精英和二級怪都是獻祭怪，需要一定的續航能力；\n\n5-4：最討厭初始造物的一集，看似抽5很强，實際會被艾繼絲二階段卡成滿手石頭 。建議使用成長陣容，一階段發育好二階段進門秒殺，也可以使用毒隊。\n常規中圖，2點2商，精英和二級怪依次是狗、蜜蜂、馬，建議使用道中足夠强大的陣容，也可以進行逃課（筆者就打了蜜蜂直接撤", "timestamp": "2024-06-10T13:40:02.222000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-12T09:20:05.034000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 10}], "attachments": [{"id": "1249719730391224331", "filename": "HAO5UY4IW75VYM609U.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 225839, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249719729665605643/1249719730391224331/HAO5UY4IW75VYM609U.png?ex=69fb44b2&is=69f9f332&hm=46f583c223e914512b93402a82be8c9d0f12f74c7460d2fa508af11467d62ff9&"}, {"id": "1249719730785353800", "filename": "9VNLW6A9YIPTEBB6N70.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 925723, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249719729665605643/1249719730785353800/9VNLW6A9YIPTEBB6N70.png?ex=69fb44b2&is=69f9f332&hm=0d61f444f190924c87b5aa55efc06e4707d211a5710ee867b267fa73993f424f&"}, {"id": "1249719731171360849", "filename": "WDFL2WUJPEMHCJD90RBF8H.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 942389, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249719729665605643/1249719731171360849/WDFL2WUJPEMHCJD90RBF8H.png?ex=69fb44b2&is=69f9f332&hm=8cc0cd4ae113a55d41a3fb83de105dc0c7374f2332e34d05b665ab676e9000a8&"}, {"id": "1249719731699712141", "filename": "5WGNFGQMNNUMSXBR.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1002383, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249719729665605643/1249719731699712141/5WGNFGQMNNUMSXBR.png?ex=69fb44b2&is=69f9f332&hm=4fe0ec31ff2bc832dad6197f874bbcc557584a49110a548a3edf5228b48ca5e4&"}, {"id": "1249719732236587019", "filename": "1LF6H3P_1R1HDQA.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 984053, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249719729665605643/1249719732236587019/1LF6H3P_1R1HDQA.png?ex=69fb44b2&is=69f9f332&hm=b2de02f75abe1e96a13d8b04f15e528c3064001ed10d6a5ce2ce62ee91be0ec7&"}, {"id": "1249719732903477399", "filename": "WX002JROEOD0TNMT3EG.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 959666, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249719729665605643/1249719732903477399/WX002JROEOD0TNMT3EG.png?ex=69fb44b2&is=69f9f332&hm=17700cbfddd2b368f7c0ffdabd79702237fdd9c7895564a307b4691afac193bd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1249719729665605643", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "第二期融灾375攻略（325、350也可參考）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1249569598882316369", "channel_id": "1249569598882316369", "type": 0, "author_id": "960513153240825907", "author_name": "dyyqcwj", "author_bot": false, "content": "我避开了所有限定SSR角色和命轮，包括活动SR命轮！只有6个是需要抽取的SSR命轮，并且因为我练度较高，我的作战过程都没有爆死抗，压力比较大的2-2留了300死抗，包括惩戒都没有用！希望能够对即将打325分的萌新有帮助，视频全流程均上传B站，有疑惑点可以留言，我尽量回复的", "timestamp": "2024-06-10T03:43:28.254000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 11}], "attachments": [{"id": "1249569599364530258", "filename": "Screenshot_20240610_113940_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 213217, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249569598882316369/1249569599364530258/Screenshot_20240610_113940_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb61a0&is=69fa1020&hm=2828311bf6e9cc48a23bca589c26606e22b22774edd53a121c6ae82e75e603a9&"}, {"id": "1249569599683432448", "filename": "Screenshot_20240610_111850_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 210222, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249569598882316369/1249569599683432448/Screenshot_20240610_111850_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb61a0&is=69fa1020&hm=b822fae426c1f56be3e14143337fefbf2f283d51274fd8ee7991527347358081&"}, {"id": "1249569600010584145", "filename": "Screenshot_20240610_113947_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 209504, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249569598882316369/1249569600010584145/Screenshot_20240610_113947_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb61a0&is=69fa1020&hm=a3104783a85109db18c11c8238013bf1e82f544905d45a6c0af70eb302dc2287&"}, {"id": "1249569600429883443", "filename": "Screenshot_20240610_113951_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 215188, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249569598882316369/1249569600429883443/Screenshot_20240610_113951_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb61a0&is=69fa1020&hm=6ba593faa7a687af294396063403a941bf4b760ad1f952d165980c8fa2e81a34&"}, {"id": "1249569600794923068", "filename": "Screenshot_20240610_113956_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 211190, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249569598882316369/1249569600794923068/Screenshot_20240610_113956_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb61a0&is=69fa1020&hm=859795ac43c7ddbe1de10a37d27d599e4acbae6e83fecaf009ba6a01e635a761&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1249569598882316369", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "为萌新打造的融灾325无限定攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1243105047332524043", "1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1249807256875434067", "channel_id": "1249807256875434067", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家好，這裡是難忘今宵攻略組，本期為大家帶來的是第10期「融灾禁區」地圖。\n◆每兩周重繪獎勵與關卡，每個關卡只需要完成其中一個難度即可。\n◆經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除血量上限的約5%，也就是固定值。\n當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判斷為致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n◆同一關卡的Ⅰ級警報、Ⅱ級警報、Ⅲ級警報和Ⅳ警報的地圖都相同。\n▼▼▼\n【第1波】意識潜遊-珊「如歌的雕琢」-見信如晤地圖\n【第2波】意識潜遊-旺達「燃燒的群宴」-四個婚禮地圖\n【第3波】無光之境-混沌之域·輪轉間隙Ⅱ（1.13）地圖\n【第4波】第7期融灾禁區·第4波地圖\n【第5波】意識潜遊-奧瑞塔「諸事如常」-朋友大收集地圖\n也就是和第7期一模一樣，放個7期連接：https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1235295785919451278\n另，第4波地圖左上角加了個事件（不知道是這次新加的還是上次忘加了）。\nuid100001547", "timestamp": "2024-06-10T19:27:50.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-10T19:31:14.608000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1249807257395396700", "filename": "Image_1718047073846.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 282217, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249807256875434067/1249807257395396700/Image_1718047073846.jpg?ex=69fb9636&is=69fa44b6&hm=5a91bc7b638b2b11cc8dd54fb334836f3d73acbcf0a3baaf65030da227cae030&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1249807256875434067", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關卡地圖「融灾禁區」總覽Ⅹ", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043"]}
{"id": "1249810574767034530", "channel_id": "1249810574767034530", "type": 0, "author_id": "1212784185639567390", "author_name": "kirot0150", "author_bot": false, "content": "直接化为死抗高手🤓\n\n\n1-3打的好不如抗的多，双暴造物有莉莉会很舒服，可惜我没有，只能爆死抗了\n\n\n2-3应该是比较简单的一关，深海或者旺达叠盾抗住就行，可以留在最后打，地图症状多，可以带消除症状的r卡。\n\n\n3-3最折磨的一集，没练宁妃，带上宁妃叠毒应该很轻松，24开了十几个大才磨死boss，注意boss多段技能就行\n\n\n4-3开五次大boss就会放大招还招小怪，油污现在就能很好的解决这个问题，而且油污不吃boss的封印，就很舒服，道中带上蜘蛛和神父可以很好的保证血量，boss关只需要开油污和羊妈大招就行\n\n5-3注意别在boss二阶段拖太久就行，艾继丝一阶段伤害不高而且给的迟缓也少，在一阶段生生胎，然后进二阶段红花一套秒就行。", "timestamp": "2024-06-10T19:41:01.382000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-10T19:41:50.564000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1249810575517810818", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-10-19-50-33-83_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 163533, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810575517810818/Screenshot_2024-06-10-19-50-33-83_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69faf08d&is=69f99f0d&hm=cedcfd223aae24a1f24572f973427a0fbaf32dccf83e56cd7904c2b34d23a250&"}, {"id": "1249810575811149885", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-17-34_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 158335, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810575811149885/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-17-34_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69faf08d&is=69f99f0d&hm=15aa522dcaeb3391ad045acd2f34d85ad8d788140a020ff95a9a98f529746479&"}, {"id": "1249810576184709140", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-20-25_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 162458, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810576184709140/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-20-25_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69faf08d&is=69f99f0d&hm=7c44874b343759401c09c57a6c90735dc24be2a0c87b5e3cff475e3edc1a9030&"}, {"id": "1249810576545284217", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-22-97_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 157501, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810576545284217/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-22-97_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69faf08d&is=69f99f0d&hm=4d13c9ce607fcab1d987d43b9644a92b55a1774f988f0c99554567582a7f2674&"}, {"id": "1249810576897609850", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-26-51_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 165301, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810576897609850/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-26-51_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69faf08d&is=69f99f0d&hm=2687b6967edf0802d253be84fdaeb0bdaa5fabc9a66f0afae211f25655d40c4a&"}, {"id": "1249810577182691449", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-29-87_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 162357, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1249810574767034530/1249810577182691449/Screenshot_2024-06-11-03-11-29-87_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69faf08d&is=69f99f0d&hm=b5dd7a5de49d6f485ae5a74d39cbb03c3a8b64e4b8d6ea6a21a34b52d13ef429&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1249810574767034530", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "这期融灾350参考", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1243105047332524043"]}
